chat.msg: hey, q tal? empezamos el juego?
si - listo
brilliant! I am next to the starting point, I see a twig to the left that leads to an island with a tiger
Where am I headed, friend?
a el tigre
all right, using the twig to get to the tiger
now, where to?
to the parrot
Bien, yendo al suroeste hacia la isla con un loro y un árbol, veo el loro, ¿adónde vamos ahora?
Ve hacia las rocas, que conducen hacia la rana verde.
perfect, I go southeast towards the 3 rocks and now I am in front of the island with the frog
What comes after the green frog?
hay un cocodrilo frente a una gran roca. ¡Sigue al cocodrilo y verás una jirafa justo encima de las dos rocas siguientes!
whoa, watch out for that croc! moving west past our new reptilian friend now
woah, there's that giraffe! what's our next stop?
next, there is a boa constrictor hanging from a branch
¡Entendido, en dirección sureste, serpiente avistada! ¿Adónde vamos ahora?
y ahora, al cofre del tesoro :)
ah, the treasure chest, moving 2 steps east
all right, i see the treasure. *finished* we made it, pal!

chat.msg: hola, you ready?
si!

cool! gotcha right next to the white dog? now let's take a small stroll towards the left, below a wooden bench to a florist stand. but we aren't stopping there, just make a u-turn before getting there, cross the trail again and head back towards mr.
white dog. how's that for a warm up?!
all good :)
now where to?!
¡asombroso! Ahora, vayamos hacia el sur, crucemos el ramal hacia otro perro blanco que está haciendo un picnic.
¿Te importaría unirte a él por un segundo?
¡Oki Doki! Continúe pasando al perro, sobre la alfombra de picnic y recoja una baya, guiñándole un ojo al siguiente perro blanco.
¿Lo ves a el? ¡Ahora dirijamos hacia el oeste!
Genial, estoy aquí y lista para la próxima instrucción
fantastic! Do you see a wooden track that crosses the river to the north? let's take that
okay, im now facing the lorist stand, and there is a bridge to my left with some people on a bicicleta
florist**
gotcha! now, let's give the green bush a wide berth, circling around it from the right, head to the florist stand, don't touch anything yet!
¡exacto! ahora vamos a girar a la izquierda, pase por debajo del stand de flores y vaya directo al gran puente con los dos ciclistas.
ok - estoy aqui
perfección! just past the bridge there are two old folks reading newspapers, let's head towards them but just a bit south of them
do you see that other wooden branch and green bush? let's head towards it next

chat.msg: hi there! que comience el juego!!
okay, lets first head south from our tent and look for a dog stretching out by a bush!
¡está bien! dirigiéndome al sur desde la tienda ahora
oh, veo un perro junto al fuego, ¿te refieres a este?
si!!
Alright, here I am by the dog, next to the fire
What's the next move, buddy?
from there, continue south down the trail, past the red mushrooms and heading towards a blue car
¡entendido! Dirigiéndose al sur, pasando por los hongos rojos y dirigiéndose hacia el auto azul.
¿que sigue?
Desde aquí, continúa hacia el sur hasta llegar a un telescopio.
yeah, I see the blue telescope
What path should I take now?
excelente - now continue on the trail past the teelscope and there will be cabin surrounded by large rocks
genial, me dirijo por el camino pasando el telescopio hacia la cabaña rodeada de rocas
yay! we did it
buen trabajo
¡Sí lo hicimos, llegué a la casa! *terminado* ¡Esto fue divertido, amigo! hagamos esto de nuevo alguna vez
thank you! It was great working together on this.
until next time!

chat.msg: hey there, estas listo?
si - listo
brilliant! let's start then
Go southwest, go under the first palm tree, turn right and cross the second tree. then, turn sharply left before the third tree and continue south
gotcha! i see un perro
awww, cute! but don't let it distract you
take a slight left then a right towards the south, passing on the left side of the puppy
He llegado a unas rocas grandes, ¿ahora hacia dónde voy?
good job, friend! Now, find your path between the big rock on your left and the smaller one on your right, heading towards the water
el hermoso agua azul!! now that im near the water, shall i go towards the crab or towards the shark?
haha, good question! start by heading towards the crab for now
once you reach him, take a right along the big rock and move west in the water
ooooh - i spy a tiburon
oh, a shark! start getting used to 'em, mate
now, make a sharp turn on your right after you pass a medium-sized rock
back to shore, now where to, pal?
¡dulce! ¿Ves una bola azul, amarilla y blanca? Muévete hacia el norte, apretándote entre eso y la roca mediana que acabas de pasar.
¡sigue adelante!
y de vuelta a la tienda
aha! you've got the red tent and a speaker, right? let's shuffle northwest between those two
okie dokie
now, trace a little arc around that red tent and then go south
be careful not to get into the water though!
aye-aye, captain
great! now, see that red kayak? cruise along the shore and head west below the kayak
hecho :)
amazing job! now, let's finish our quest
make a 90 degrees turn to the right, head north along the kayak until you reach a small green bush
